! $Id: tdiff2,v 1.1 2001/12/07 16:54:20 toast Exp $
TDIFF2(seconds)
  Returns a string representing the number of seconds passed, similar
  to TDIFF but more abbreviated.

Example:
  tdiff2(0)		- Returns "0s"
  tdiff2(12345)		- Returns "3h 25m 45s"
  tdiff2(9825284)	- Returns "113d 17h 14m 44s"

See also:
  FUNCTIONS TDIFF
